data.description: ONTARIO RANCH continues to be a GROWING and highly DESIRABLE area!  This BEAUTIFUL 2016 built home has the space you are after to both LIVE and ENTERTAIN in.  Walking in you have an AMAZING sight line to the rear of the home showing off the flow of the HARDWOOD floors.  One bedroom with its own bathroom downstairs along with an additional powder room for guests.  The kitchen boasts, granite counters, a HUGE ISLAND and PLENTY OF STORAGE throughout. Moving upstairs the hardwood continues throughout the SIZABLE LOFT and four additional rooms including the large primary.  Primary bathroom has separated TUB and SHOWER.  Backyard has covered patio and ORANGE/POMEGRANITE/AVACADO trees to freely pull from.  When you are looking to get out of the house and enjoy the newhavenlife.com/amenities/ you will have your choice of 5 PARKS with MULTIPLE POOLS, MULTIPLE FIRE PITS, and MULTIPLE ACTIVITIES!  New Haven really puts your LOW HOA dollars to work and invests in YOUR WELLBEING! With the FUTURE plans of the GREAT PARK in Ontario right down the street, you will not lack for things to do. Come see why this home is PERFECT for you!
